Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許你倆結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.35,0:01:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告地球上的全體人類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乃奇多·路西翁·戴比路克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙的支配者是也
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥組隊長向各機通告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除安全裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄徒勞的抵抗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你們所看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們戴比路克星人能在一瞬間把你們變成宇宙的塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並沒有要侵略的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  給我乖乖的看著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言歸正傳  好久不見啊  菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有很多要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過先要把事情解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙和我約定要成為宇宙第一的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來讓他履行約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  梨斗只是個普通的地球男孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用爸爸的標準來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情  我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙和我的男人與男人的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說這種任性的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是整個戴比路克星的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話就說到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩斯丁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  一定不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈的話  一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  我並不是菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩斯丁…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑爺大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  我是來替奇多·路西翁·戴比路克王傳話的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為菈菈·薩塔琳·戴比路克  第一公主的未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:05:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你履行和奇多·路西翁·戴比路克王的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方法如下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  將要賭上地球的命運  來玩一個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球代表是結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其內容為…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城梨斗要順利到達我的飛船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天黎明時分  遊戲開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時限是  日落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有說的必要  在到達飛船的過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會有各種各樣的考驗在等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果姑爺大人失敗了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球就將被毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你武運昌隆  姑爺大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球的命運  不知怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被交到了一個叫結城梨斗的少年的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的奇多·路西翁·戴比路克和那些UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說日本政府和美國了  全世界都在保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟日本會…不是  這個地球究竟會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們居住的這個地球  究竟會變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未來到底會怎樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道這一天總會到來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒想到這麼快…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不住  美柑  讓我一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了  能抽出點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御門老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情變得很糟糕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想關於戴比路克星人提供點建議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻也什麼都想不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴比路克王一向是個說到做到的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從很久以前就挺喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御門老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的一夜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我安慰你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  結城君  你在聽我說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你很喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  這個地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡你所能去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是…對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算一直消沉著  也不會有任何改變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  猿山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天地球就要毀滅了  你會怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說這麼不吉利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說的話  我會把存款都用完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個如果明天地球就要毀滅了  你會要吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶問一句  今天吃什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就吃了咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你究竟在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是碰巧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  咖喱放到第二天會更好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正  不要放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不一定是結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想繼續吃咖喱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜託你了  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你專門打電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是爸爸的傳真和媽媽的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}負起責任來！ 爸爸留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs19}加油！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們真是無憂無慮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子遇到這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:10:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這樣啊  他們也有他們的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然媽媽在國外工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸又被關起來趕漫畫的稿子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最後來見我一面又…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  梨斗  你不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.21,0:10:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是「相信明天不會是世界末日」的證據吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也相信  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想見結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  那麼  在那個公園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這出去是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站…起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色闇影？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候  是和菈菈一起這樣從房頂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個星球上除了梨斗我還有很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要說什麼毀滅地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給他機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這點也該感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所…以…說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎麼求我  既然對我的女兒出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要負起責任來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗並沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈大人…不管說什麼都沒用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對啊  菈菈  和我談判是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情你應該明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有不要產生其它念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能從這裡逃出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西連寺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  該我說對不起才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候還把你叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  反正睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…才是我喜歡的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  關於昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  這個  該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  結城君被菈菈吸引著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直看著的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎不…不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  根本不知道怎麼說才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候確實順勢說了喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我卻是一直對小春菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正  明天就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天  我會為了地球上的人類而奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明天能平安無事的到達戴比路克的飛船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能聽我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有點奇怪啊  顫抖個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然努力裝出平靜的樣子  實際上卻害怕的很
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子明天還…  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君的話  一定不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球代表是結城梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其內容為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天傍晚6點  戴比路克星人的宇宙飛船擊退了戰鬥機動隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然停留在新宿的上空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次  我定要改變給你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:18:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右地球命運的遊戲的帷幕在這一刻被拉開了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後勝利的究竟是人類  還是戴比路克星人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御門老師  我有事拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好輕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天還緊張到牙齒都打架的狀態簡直像假的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直跑步鍛煉也看出效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  這傢伙運氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.29,0:19:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽牛花怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間就能發芽  它的籐蔓能抓到任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦抓到了  到晚上才會放開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  越掙扎就纏得越緊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畜生！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能夠認輸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君  抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古手川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:21:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御門老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有猿山也…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是古手川同學的功勞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了昨天播出的新聞  我有發現到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,條件只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要結城君到達那艘飛船就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有說  我們不能助你一臂之力什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上性命的不止你一個人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要請我吃咖喱哦  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要誤會  我只是為了地球才這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  抓緊  要飛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美柑  糖果  很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里紗  未央  不能摸我尾巴  不要忘了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.67,0:23:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿山  要和小皮好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  我不知道風紀的意思  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.21,0:23:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫  要努力成為偶像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御門老師  謝謝您多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:23:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小闇  工作要有個限度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙姬  還想和你一起玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.95,0:24:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜  謝謝你和我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈！
